((3) 0 () 0 () () (u . "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n\n  <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/functions.js\"></script>\n\n  <meta content=\"Experience | Alexander Nabavi-Noori\" name=\"title\" />\n  <meta content=\"Alexander Nabavi-Noori's experience.\" name=\"description\" />\n  <meta content=\"website\" property=\"og:type\" />\n  <meta content=\"https://alexandernnoori.com/experience.html\" property=\"og:url\" />\n  <meta content=\"Experience | Alexander Nabavi-Noori\" property=\"og:title\" />\n  <meta content=\"Alexander Nabavi-Noori's experience.\" property=\"og:description\" />\n  <meta content=\"summary_large_image\" property=\"twitter:card\" />\n  <meta content=\"@xandernn\" property=\"twitter:site\" />\n  <meta content=\"https://alexandernnoori.com/experience.html\" property=\"twitter:url\" />\n  <meta content=\"Experience | Alexander Nabavi-Noori\" property=\"twitter:title\" />\n  <meta content=\"Alexander Nabavi-Noori's experience.\" property=\"twitter:description\" />\n\n  <link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" />\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"all\" href=\"/fonts/fonts.css\" />\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"all\" href=\"/styles.css\" />\n\n  <title>Experience | Alexander Nabavi-Noori</title>\n\n  <style type=\"text/css\">\n    #switcher {\n      margin-top: 12px;\n      border: 1px solid gray;\n      box-shadow: 2px 2px;\n      cursor: default;\n      text-align: center;\n      padding-top: 0.2em;\n      padding-bottom: 0.2em;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n\n<body id=\"body\" class=\"body-text_century-supra\">\n\n  <div id=\"switcher\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"index.html\">About</a>\n<a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"/research.html\">Research</a>\n<a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"/experience.html\">Experience</a>\n<a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"/blog.html\">Blog</a>\n<a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"/contact.html\">Contact</a>\n<a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"/ANabaviNoori_CV.pdf\">CV</a>\n</div>\n\n  <div id=\"content\">\n\n    <div id=\"doc\"><div id=\"doc\"><p><title-block><topic class=\"small\">Expe\u00ADri\u00ADence</topic><short-rule></short-rule></title-block></p><p>Before begin\u00ADning my doc\u00ADtoral work, I spent sev\u00ADeral years prac\u00ADtic\u00ADing law in and around the fed\u00ADeral gov\u00ADern\u00ADment—clerk\u00ADing for two fed\u00ADeral judges, work\u00ADing as an appel\u00ADlate attor\u00ADney at the Depart\u00ADment of Jus\u00ADtice, and advis\u00ADing on immi\u00ADgra\u00ADtion pol\u00ADicy in the Sen\u00ADate. That expe\u00ADri\u00ADence left me with a gran\u00ADu\u00ADlar sense of how fed\u00ADeral insti\u00ADtu\u00ADtions actu\u00ADally oper\u00ADate, and a set of ques\u00ADtions about bureau\u00ADcratic behav\u00ADior and admin\u00ADis\u00ADtra\u00ADtive power that I couldn’t fully answer from inside the prac\u00ADtice of law.</p><div class=\"subhead\" id=\"professional\"><a href=\"#professional\">Pro\u00ADfes\u00ADsional</a></div><aside><p>2025–2026</p></aside><p>Asso\u00ADci\u00ADate, <span class=\"font-century-supra-caps\">O’Mel\u00ADveny &amp; Myers LLP,</span> New York, NY</p><aside><p>2024–2025</p></aside><p>Appel\u00ADlate Staff Attor\u00ADney, <span class=\"font-century-supra-caps\">U.S. Depart\u00ADment of Jus\u00ADtice, Civil Divi\u00ADsion</span></p><aside><p>2023–2024</p></aside><p>Law Clerk to Judge Cor\u00ADnelia T.L. Pil\u00ADlard, <span class=\"font-century-supra-caps\">U.S. Court of Appeals for the D.C. Cir\u00ADcuit</span></p><aside><p>2022–2023</p></aside><p>Law Clerk to Chief Judge James E. Boas\u00ADberg, <span class=\"font-century-supra-caps\">U.S. Dis\u00ADtrict Court for the Dis\u00ADtrict of Colum\u00ADbia</span></p><aside><p>2021–2022</p></aside><p>Spe\u00ADcial Assis\u00ADtant and Yale Law School Hey\u00ADman Fel\u00ADlow to Sen. Blu\u00ADmen\u00ADthal, <span class=\"font-century-supra-caps\">U.S. Sen\u00ADate Judi\u00ADciary Com\u00ADmit\u00ADtee</span></p><aside><p>Sum\u00ADmer 2020</p></aside><p>Sum\u00ADmer Asso\u00ADci\u00ADate, <span class=\"font-century-supra-caps\">Jen\u00ADner &amp; Block LLP</span></p><aside><p>Sum\u00ADmer 2019</p></aside><p>Appel\u00ADlate Staff Intern, <span class=\"font-century-supra-caps\">U.S. Depart\u00ADment of Jus\u00ADtice, Civil Divi\u00ADsion</span></p><div class=\"subhead\" id=\"teaching\"><a href=\"#teaching\">Teach\u00ADing</a></div><aside><p>Fall 2019</p></aside><p>Teach\u00ADing Fel\u00ADlow, <span class=\"font-century-supra-caps\">PLSC 233: Con\u00ADsti\u00ADtu\u00ADtional Law</span>, <span class=\"no-hyphens\">Yale Col\u00ADlege</span></p><div class=\"indented\">Instruc\u00ADtor: Akhil Reed Amar</div></div></div><a id=\"links\"></a>\n    <div class=\"gap\" style=\"height:1em\"></div>\n    <ul class=\"children\"></ul>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div id=\"toolbar\" class=\"\">\n\n    <div id=\"navtable\">\n\n      <div>\n        <a class=\"box-link\" href=\"colophon.html\"><span class=\"arrow\">←</span>&nbsp;colophon</a>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"center\">\n        <a class=\"box-link\" href=\"/\">home</a>\n      </div>\n\n      <div>\n        <a class=\"box-link\" href=\"/ANabaviNoori_CV.pdf\">curriculum vitae&nbsp;<span class=\"arrow\">→</span></a>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>"))